    <item>
      <title>据《海峡时报》报道，华侨银行出售与新加坡洗钱丑闻有关的圣淘沙土地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ocbc-sells-sentosa-land-tied-to-singapore-laundering-scandal-st-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《海峡时报》报道，华侨银行已接受一份超过 2000 万新元（1500 万美元）的报价，收购圣淘沙湾一块地皮。该地皮是从一名涉嫌新加坡最大洗钱案的罪犯手中夺取的。但《海峡时报》并未透露这一消息来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ocbc-sells-sentosa-land-tied-to-singapore-laundering-scandal-st-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 23:45:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
